nodes.text: Warehouse 305 was a warehouse managed by the Rodian Yilon Kres. During the Clone Wars, an underworld operative who went by the alias "Mera Mal" sent a group of individuals to retrieve fifty cases of Corellian Run MultiMeals and deliver them to the bio-dome city Ronion on the planet Mandalore.

Warehouse 305 was mentioned in the 2020 roleplaying game sourcebook Collapse of the Republic, in an adventure seed for Fantasy Flight Games' Star Wars Roleplaying. The sourcebook states that the warehouse can be located anywhere that is convenient for the campaign.
